BT /F2 15 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 645.00 Tm (8. Challenges & Solutions) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 608.00 Tm (Challenge 1: Supporting Different Learning Needs) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 592.00 Tm (The project needs to support students who may respond better to visual, audio, or text-based) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 578.00 Tm (learning.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 557.00 Tm (Solution:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 543.00 Tm (The system collects multiple indicators and predicts a learning style. It also provides) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 529.00 Tm (separate recommendation maps for Visual, Audio, and Text learners.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 502.00 Tm (Challenge 2: Combining ML Prediction With Behavioral Support) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 486.00 Tm (Learning style alone does not explain all student needs.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 465.00 Tm (Solution:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 451.00 Tm (The frontend adds behavior tracking and timed support-check tasks. Rule-based insight) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 437.00 Tm (functions convert behavior patterns into practical support suggestions.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 410.00 Tm (Challenge 3: Backend Availability) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 394.00 Tm (The frontend depends on the Flask API for prediction.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 373.00 Tm (Solution:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 359.00 Tm (The frontend includes mockPrediction\(\) as a fallback so the app can still show a result if) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 345.00 Tm (the backend is unavailable.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 318.00 Tm (Challenge 4: Handling Missing Dataset Values) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 302.00 Tm (The dataset contains missing values in some columns.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 281.00 Tm (Solution:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 267.00 Tm (Training scripts fill numeric columns with mean values and categorical columns with mode or) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 253.00 Tm (Unknown.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 226.00 Tm (Challenge 5: Feature Alignment Between Training and Inference) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 210.00 Tm (ML models require prediction-time features to match training-time features.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 189.00 Tm (Solution:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 175.00 Tm (The backend defines a fixed FEATURES list and reads incoming request values in that exact) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 161.00 Tm (order. The training script also saves feature_names.pkl for reference.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 134.00 Tm (Challenge 6: Making Reports Understandable) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 118.00 Tm (ML outputs can be difficult for non-technical users.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 97.00 Tm (Solution:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 83.00 Tm (The frontend translates raw features and scores into plain-language interpretations for) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 69.00 Tm (parents and teachers.) Tj ET
endstream
