BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 661.00 Tm (- Add frontend tests using a React testing framework.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 647.00 Tm (- Standardize one preprocessing pipeline for training and inference.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 633.00 Tm (- Add model versioning and metadata.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 619.00 Tm (- Add authentication checks before saving reports.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 605.00 Tm (- Add teacher/admin dashboard for reviewing multiple students.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 591.00 Tm (- Improve accessibility with keyboard navigation audits and screen-reader labels.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 577.00 Tm (- Add export options for reports, such as PDF or printable HTML.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 546.00 Tm (11. Summary) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 515.00 Tm (This project is an adaptive learning system that helps students discover the study format) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 501.00 Tm (that may suit them best. It asks questions, observes learning behavior, runs short support) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 487.00 Tm (tasks, and uses a machine learning model to predict whether the student may benefit most from) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 473.00 Tm (visual, audio, or text-based learning. The app then turns that result into practical) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 459.00 Tm (recommendations, charts, and a parent/teacher report, making the output useful for both) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 445.00 Tm (students and the adults supporting them.) Tj ET
endstream
